0fb6d4ed-9537-4fe5-9d27-ee5861f4c074.title: Hetty
0fb6d4ed-9537-4fe5-9d27-ee5861f4c074.text: What could you want with an old woman like me?

options.text: I am in search of a quest.
I've heard that you are a witch.

daccf5ba-481e-42f3-8b0f-b1af3de4ba7e.title: <player>
daccf5ba-481e-42f3-8b0f-b1af3de4ba7e.text: I've heard that you are a witch.

b2f85d66-042a-4315-839c-fca83604966c.title: Hetty
b2f85d66-042a-4315-839c-fca83604966c.text:
Yes it does seem to be getting fairly common
knowledge.

000779ac-f3b1-4fa9-951e-3c20580c06cb.title: Hetty
000779ac-f3b1-4fa9-951e-3c20580c06cb.text:
I fear I may get a visit from the witch hunters of
Falador before long.

448214b5-d15c-4081-a473-535ecfce2719.title: <player>
448214b5-d15c-4081-a473-535ecfce2719.text: I am in search of a quest.

dfa8732d-efb4-490a-840a-118d263833b4.title: Hetty
dfa8732d-efb4-490a-840a-118d263833b4.text: Hmmm... Maybe I can think of something for you.

00b714f2-955d-4b09-a138-e4e2a4cea6e0.title: Hetty
00b714f2-955d-4b09-a138-e4e2a4cea6e0.text:
Would you like to become a more proficient in the dark
arts?

options.text: Yes help me become one with my darker side.
No I have my principles and honour.
What, you mean improve my magic?

4af6f8dd-73f8-4153-833e-7c0f8c478e6e.title: <player>
4af6f8dd-73f8-4153-833e-7c0f8c478e6e.text: Yes help me become one with my darker side.

eff3233e-3210-49e3-a129-964a9e272dce.title: Hetty
eff3233e-3210-49e3-a129-964a9e272dce.text:
Ok I'm going to make a potion to help bring out your
darker self.

259e0436-5214-4483-b5fe-e35ec17d09dc.title: Hetty
259e0436-5214-4483-b5fe-e35ec17d09dc.text:
You need an eye of newt, a rat's tail, an onion... OH
and a piece of burnt meat.

c40db2d2-3019-4987-9d8b-d5f53252ff00.title: <player>
c40db2d2-3019-4987-9d8b-d5f53252ff00.text: Great, I'll go and get them.

7e0afec2-51b3-4da7-81a2-2d581c5f7e2e.title: <player>
7e0afec2-51b3-4da7-81a2-2d581c5f7e2e.text: No I have my principles and honour.

cc094f3a-6be4-4641-919a-6ee0439eafe7.title: Hetty
cc094f3a-6be4-4641-919a-6ee0439eafe7.text: Suit yourself, but you're missing out.

d7a7c6d5-8713-4f5f-b14e-880c9eb3d4e5.title: <player>
d7a7c6d5-8713-4f5f-b14e-880c9eb3d4e5.text: What, you mean improve my magic?

b390953a-7f53-4c27-bc32-936f1a92696d.title: Hetty
b390953a-7f53-4c27-bc32-936f1a92696d.text: Do you have no sense of drama?

options.text: Yes I'd like to improve my magic.
Show me the mysteries of the dark arts...

3d66b940-b71f-40bb-b7ae-d066d9d4e895.title: <player>
3d66b940-b71f-40bb-b7ae-d066d9d4e895.text: Yes I'd like to improve my magic.

cd50579f-d59a-4e13-af2d-f90a1be86b0c.title: <player>
cd50579f-d59a-4e13-af2d-f90a1be86b0c.text: Show me the mysteries of the dark arts...

ef6f35f3-0dc7-4d42-a37d-53e15750c516.title: Hetty
ef6f35f3-0dc7-4d42-a37d-53e15750c516.text: Excellent, can I have them then?

16203495-20db-4002-abab-af6da8970bb6.text:
You pass the ingredients to Hetty and she puts them all into her
cauldron. Hetty closes her eyes and begins to chant. The cauldron
bubbles mysteriously.

5f38b66e-197c-4174-a931-cd17acb77647.title: Hetty
5f38b66e-197c-4174-a931-cd17acb77647.text: Ok, now drink from the cauldron.

fd18f827-d7fe-4043-82fe-e625b013ff68.title: Hetty
fd18f827-d7fe-4043-82fe-e625b013ff68.text: So have you found the things for the potion?

32239f1a-7d1e-4290-83fe-2e6cdcad5f58.title: <player>
32239f1a-7d1e-4290-83fe-2e6cdcad5f58.text: I have found some of the things you asked for:

ad469105-c3c3-4ee3-86c4-fb1c5980c79f.title: Hetty
ad469105-c3c3-4ee3-86c4-fb1c5980c79f.text: Great, but I'll need the other ingredients as well.

6c93689d-1019-4e38-843d-f7348520d01b.title: Hetty
6c93689d-1019-4e38-843d-f7348520d01b.text: So have you found the things for the potion?

44ff537a-f6a9-4fbd-bc7c-05e437c2b4ad.title: Hetty
44ff537a-f6a9-4fbd-bc7c-05e437c2b4ad.text:
Well I can't make a potion without the ingredients. I
need an eye of newt, a rat's tail, an onion and a piece
of burnt meat.

bc147ad4-2cbf-486b-a9ee-06e174d7f287.title: Hetty
bc147ad4-2cbf-486b-a9ee-06e174d7f287.text: Well are you going to drink the potion or not?

dbb348f8-22cd-4d61-a6ce-60000c3c6256.title: <player>
dbb348f8-22cd-4d61-a6ce-60000c3c6256.text: I'm practicing and slowly getting better.
